reviewText: I didn't getting a copy that will work in Australian based computers, even I returned and got a new copy, and on top of that I found it is not Argentine Tango is American Tango that is a poor imitation of the real one. I just wasted my money on it.

It is listed as DVD
but it is 1 DVD and 1 CD
the DVD is  short how to Tango bad
the CD is not the best
I thought I would get a good Vido

Not what I expected.  Liked the music CD but the instructional DVD was that of American Tango, not Argentine Tango with confusing language navigation.  I kept the music CD and donated the DVD. I'm usually very happy with all your products with this exception.
